productDetails.name: Infinix NOTE 8i(X683)-6.78"HD+ INFINITY-O DISPLAY-64GB ROM/4GB ROM-8MP+48MP/2MP/2MP/AI LENS-5200MAH-OBSIDIAN BLACK
productDetails.description: Infinix Note 8 and Note 8i have been launched by the Shenzhen-based company at a virtual event. Both models come with quad rear cameras and are powered by MediaTek Helio G80 SoC. The Infinix Note 8 and Note 8i also feature a hd+ infinity-o display, with the Note 8 featuring dual selfie cameras. For an enhanced audio experience, the Infinix Note 8 and Note 8i come with DTS Audio processing. The Infinix Note 8 also comes with dual speakers to deliver stereo audio. The dual-SIM (Nano) Infinix Note 8i runs on Android TM10 and features a 6.78-inch HD+ (720x1,640 pixels) IPS display with a 20.5:9 aspect ratio. The phone is powered by the MediaTek Helio G80 SoC, paired with 4GB of RAM. It comes with the quad rear camera setup that includes a 48-megapixel primary sensor, 2-megapixel macro shooter, 2-megapixel depth sensor, and an AI lens. For selfies, the Note 8i offers a single 8-megapixel camera sensor at the front, along with dual LED flash. Infinix has given 64GB of onboard storage that is expandable via microSD card (up to 128GB) through a dedicated slot. Connectivity options include 4G LTE, Wi-Fi 802.11ac, Bluetooth, GPS/ A-GPS, USB Type-C, and a 3.5mm headphone jack. Sensors on board include an accelerometer, ambient light, magnetometer, and a proximity sensor. There is also a side-mounted fingerprint sensor.The Infinix Note 8i includes a 5,200mAh battery that supports 18W fast charging. Lastly, the phone measures 171.4x77.7x8.9mm.PRODUCT DETAILS: MEMORY 64GB ROM/4GB RAM, PROCESSOR HELIO G80, CONNECTIVITY GPS/WIFI/BT, NETWORK 4G/3G/2G, BATTERY CAPACITY 5200MAH, DIMENSION 171.4*77.7*8.9MM, OPERATING SYSTEM ANDROID TM 10, DISPLAY 6.78" HD+ INFINITY-O DISPLAY, CAMERA  8MP FF WITH DUAL FLASH LIGHT/ 48MP+2MP+2MP+AI LENS ULTRA NIGHT QUAD CAMERA WITH QUAD FLASH LIGHT, RESOLUTION 720*1640 , SENSOR  G-SENSOR/E-COMPASS/L-SENSOR/PROXIMITY SENSOR/FINGERPRINT/SOFT-GYROSCOPE
